o to <strong>Appearance > Menu</strong>, and click on screen options in the top right corner. Then check the Link Target option.<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.snilesh.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/02/wp_nav_menu_open_in_window.jpg\" alt=\"wp_nav_menu_open_in_window\" width=\"550\" height=\"156\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-1901\" /></p>\n<p>After you enable link target option from screen options settings you will find dropdown added to each menu item to set target.<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.snilesh.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/02/new_window_wp_menu.jpg\" alt=\"new_window_wp_menu\" width=\"429\" height=\"223\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-1902\" /></p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:100:\"http://www.snilesh.com/wordpress-snippets/open-wordpress-custom-menu-link-in-new-window-or-tab/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1:{s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1:\"0\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:3;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:51:\"\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n				\n		\n		\n		\n\n		\n		\n				\n			\n		\n		\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:5:{s:0:\"\";a:7:{s:5:\"title\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:57:\"wordpress qtranslate plugin get current selected language\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:100:\"http://www.snilesh.com/wordpress-snippets/wordpress-qtranslate-plugin-get-current-selected-language/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explici