con upload from options panel!</li>\n<li>Possibility to change the page background and title backgrounds from options panel</li>\n<li>25 useful shortcodes</li>\n<li>Possibility to change all the validation messages for the contact form from options panel</li>\n<li>Disable the landing module/contact module from options panel</li>\n<li>Create your custom sections using the available shortcodes</li>\n<li>Two page templates are available (Home Page and the Default Template)</li>\n<li>Unlimited portfolio categories</li>\n<li>Two custom WordPress menus</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>HTML CSS3 Features</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Pure CSS3 , 64 buttons that enlarge to suit your text and never break.</li>\n<li>Pure CSS3 , Table with animation.</li>\n<li>Google API Fonts for very fast loading!</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>jQuery Features</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Uniquely AWESOME GADGET ANIMATIONS !</li>\n<li>Dropdown Animated Menu.</li>\n<li>Animated Thumbs.</li>\n<li>Gallery Image Hover Effects</li>\n<li>2 jQuery Galleries with animated thumbnails and ColorBox Gallery.</li>\n<li>jQuery Filtrable Gallery.</li>\n<li>Working Contact Form With Field Validation.</li>\n<li>Google Maps Support!</li>\n<li>jQuery Image Zoom Integration.</li>\n</ul>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:79:\"http://wordpressskins.org/1736/worktropia-wordpress-theme-html5-css3.html/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1:{s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1:\"0\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:2;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:81:\"\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n				\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n\n		\n		\n				\n			\n		\n		\";s: