 alt=\"\" width=\"616\" height=\"397\" /></a></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<h2>Visual Shortcodes Editor</h2>\n<p>Bloom comes with a built-in visual shortcodes editor where you can preview the appearance of the page. Draw the page your way before anyone sees!</p>\n<h2>Fully Widgetized Homepage / Footer</h2>\n<p>Build your homepage with an incredible ease using the 10 custom Desginare widgets created exclusively for this theme.</p>\n<h2>Unlimited Portfolios</h2>\n<p>This theme come with a custom projects Structure where you can manage differents portfolios and respective projects.<br />\nYou can create unlimited portfolios and inside the portfolios you can create unlimited projects.</p>\n<h2>SEO optimized</h2>\n<p>Bloom has been prepared not only for user, but for search engines as well. All headings has been made in order (h1, h2, h3, &#8230;, h6) from the most important to less. You can easily customize the SEO info like the site title, keywords and description.</p>\n<h2>Theme Features</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>Clean and OnePage Design</li>\n<li>Responsive Layout</li>\n<li>Unlimited Filterable Portfolios</li>\n<li>Display work with 2 different galleries</li>\n<li>Easily Create and Manage Photo and Video Collections</li>\n<li>Unlimited Color Skins</li>\n<li>SEO optimized</li>\n<li>Extensive Options Panel</li>\n<li>30+ Awesome Visual Shortcodes</li>\n<li>10 Custom and Exclusive Widgets</li>\n<li>2 Custom Post Structures (Projects and Testimonials)</li>\n<li>Working Ajax Contact Form</li>\n<li>Full WordPress 3.3 compatibility</li>\n<li>Translation Ready</li>\n<li>XML File with the Bloom WordPress demo</li>\n<li>Layered PSD Files</li>\n<li>and much more…</li>\n</ul>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:74:\"http://wordpressskins.org/1723/bloom-responsive-wordpress-theme.html/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_ba