u can add up to 5 images for every slider + caption and link for every image.</p>\n<p><strong>Custom Backgrounds</strong> – Sympathico allows you to add a custom background image for each individual page, post and portfolio project, it dosen’t matter the size of the image you add</p>\n<p><strong>Contact and Comments</strong> – Both forms comes with and impressive jQuery validation , check out the comments.</p>\n<p><strong>Logo</strong> – I know how important is the logo, so with Sympathico, your logo can have any size, it dosen’t matter, how small or big is your logo, you’ll see that your logo will fit with the theme, if you need to change the width or the hight, and give it more margin, everything will be done from Theme Option.</p>\n<p><strong>Layout</strong> – From Theme Options ( a new one ) you can choose your layout Wide or Boxed, and ofcouse a lot more, you can play with the 6 predefined skins, choose a pattern from 18, or you can add your own pattern or background, it’s up to you, you can create your own skin ( unlimited colors ), or you can paste some custom style.</p>\n<p><strong>HTML5 + CSS3 </strong>– Modern design with modern HTML5 tags, it is compatible with all major browsers.</p>\n<p><strong>SEO </strong>– The main content block is placed before the sidebar, so will be crawled first by the search engines. All tags have been used properly for images, headings and so on. A sitemap is used for the theme ( and will be more easy for the search engines to index all the posts ), and for every page, post and portfolio project is assigned the H1 tag.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<div class=\"wpthemes_image_preview\"><a href=\"http://themeforest.net/item/sympathico-premium-wordpress-theme-/full_screen_preview/2399891?ref=neel\" title=\"Download \"Sympathico &#8211; Premium WordPress Theme\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"http://wordpressskins.org/wp-content/themes/wpskinsnew/timthumb.php?src=http://wordpressskins.org/wp-content/uploads/2012/06/01_preview.__large_preview-12.jpg&a=t&w=500\"a lt=\"Sympathico &#8211; Premium WordPress Theme\" /></a></div>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<h3>Some Features.</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>HTML5 &amp; CSS3</li>\n<li>18 background patterns</li>\n<li>3 background decorations</li>\n<li>jQuery Sliders for all pages, post and portfolio project</li>\n<li>Custom background image for all pages, post and portfolio project.</li>\n<li>6 premade colors</li>\n<li>Filterable portfolio / 2,3 and 4 columns</li>\n<li>Standard portfolio with pagination / 2,3 and 4 columns</li>\n<li>jQuery Contact Form and Comments Form with validation</li>\n<li>9 custom widgets\n<ul>\n<li>Twitter</li>\n<li>Popular Posts</li>\n<li>Last Posts</li>\n<li>Flickr</li>\n<li>Subscribe</li>\n<li>Comment with title</li>\n<li>Comments with excerpts</li>\n<li>Video YouTube</li>\n<li>Video Vimeo</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>11 sidebar areas</li>\n<li>Friendly options panel</li>\n<li>Custom Post Types : Portfolio</li>\n<li>Trun on/off the big footer</li>\n<li>Post thumbnail support with dynamic image resizing ( No More timthumb )</li>\n<li>User friendly shortcodes +50</li>\n<li>Unlimited colors</li>\n<li>Translation from Theme Options</li>\n<li>2 Layered PSDs for Customisation</li>\n<li>XML file</li>\n</ul>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:76:\"http://wordpressskins.org/1717/sympathico-premium-wordpress-theme.html/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1:{s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1:\"0\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:7;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:87:\"\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n				\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n\n		\n		\n				\n			\n		\n		\";s:7:\"attrib