"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:5:\"staff\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:5825:\"<p>Freestyle is a <strong>fully featured Responsive theme</strong>. As an addition we’ve prepared <strong>Five Beautiful Content Example Pages</strong> that are ready to use to make your pixel perfect presentation.</p>\n<p>Theme uses <strong>unique rounded images on blog and service boxes</strong>. Precise and user friendly admin panel allows you to do a lot of customizations without knowing any HTML or CSS . Colors, images, fonts, widgets, sliders, portfolios, galleries,&#8230; everything can be customized and configured via admin panel.</p>\n<p>Theme is built on our robust MVC framework that means that HTML design is completely separated from other PHP ! Making updates cannot be easier. Template &amp; MVC framework will be under continuous improvement. Purchase the theme and get all updates for free.</p>\n<p>Freestyle WordPress Theme comes also with customer support and after purchase service. We’ll do our best to answer all of your questions in a professional manner. Purchase this theme with confidence knowing that we’ll always be here to answer all of your questions.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<div class=\"wpthemes_image_preview\"><a href=\"http://themeforest.net/item/freestyle-responsive-wordpress-theme/full_screen_preview/2396575?ref=neel\" title=\"Download \"Freestyle Responsive WordPress Theme\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"http://wordpressskins.org/wp-content/themes/wpskinsnew/timthumb.php?src=http://wordpressskins.org/wp-content/uploads/2012/06/01_preview.__large_preview18.jpg&a=t&w=500\"a lt=\"Freestyle Responsive WordPress Theme\" /></a></div>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<h3>Main features are:</h3>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>5 Beautiful Content Example Pages</strong> – specially designed for this theme</li>\n<li><strong>Responsive design</strong> – works perfectly on mobile devices</li>\n<li><strong>Service boxes</strong> can be used on any page for product or services presentation</li>\n<li><strong>Many admin panel options</strong> really tells you can customize everything! No need to know HTML or CSS .</li>\n<li>You can easily <strong>Backup</strong> all your data and admin settings</li>\n<li><strong>HTML5 </strong>wordpress theme</li>\n<li><strong>Translation Ready</strong> easy translation to any other language using WPML plugin. Just have a look at our demo site.</li>\n<li><strong>MVC templating engine</strong> html templates are completely separated from PHP files, you just have to see it</li>\n<li><strong> Easy Adminisreation</strong> only with options you really need</li>\n<li><strong>Over 200 Fonts</strong> that can be also easily selected in our admin panel</li>\n<li><strong>Many portfolio layouts</strong></li>\n<li><strong>Unlimited color settings</strong> for almost everything using our easy to use admin panel</li>\n<li><strong>Everything is styled</strong> – tables, headers, paragraphs, images, lists, etc. You won’t need to fix it yourself!</li>\n<li><strong>Many many  shortcode</strong> for professional looking pages in no time</li>\n<li><strong>Shortcodes generator</strong> directly from WYSIWYG editor</li>\n<li><strong>Widgets ready</strong> sidebar &amp; footer</li>\n<li><strong>Frontend Themebox</strong> that will allows you changing colors directly from frontend while you’re looking at it</li>\n<li><strong>Image &amp; Template caching</strong> for better performance</li>\n<li><strong>Google Analytics &amp; Google Maps</strong> ready</li>\n<li><strong>Custom CSS </strong>integration</li>\n<li><strong>AIT Dashboard</strong> Documentation, FAQ , Theme support and recent updates accessible directly from our wordpress admin panel</li>\n<li><strong>Admin branding</strong> allows to you to upload your own logo, colors &amp; texts into admin.</li>\n<li><strong>White label admin</strong> individual admin options can be turned off using config.php file including AIT Dashboard.</li>\n<li><strong>Timthumb</strong> library for nice thumbnails</li>\n</ul>\n<h3>What will you also get?</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>Support on our support forum</li>\n<li>WordPress 3.x template</li>\n<li>XML Demo content</li>\n<li>PSD files</li>\n<li>Detailed documentation &amp; video tutorials</li>\n</ul>\n<h3>Versions</h3>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>v1.6 – 19th of June 2012:</strong>\n<ul>\n<li>CSS fixes</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li><strong>v1.5 – 18th of June 2012:</strong>\n<ul>\n<li>Sidebar fixes.</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li><strong>v1.4 – 14th of June 2012:</strong>\n<ul>\n<li>Fix for Android devices</li>\n<li>WordPress SEO plugin fix</li>\n<li>Theme updates notifications</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li><strong>v1.3 – 4th of June 2012:</strong>\n<ul>\n<li>Small CSS fix for share button</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li><strong>v1.2 – 30th of May 2012:</strong>\n<ul>\n<li>Search results styles fix</li>\n<li>Typo in admin panel</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li><strong>v1.1 – 25th of May 2012:</strong>\n<ul>\n<li>Minor CSS fixes for iPad</li>\n<li>Fix for main navigation to work with javascript turned off</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li><strong>v1.0 – 24th of May 2012:</strong>\n<ul>\n<li>Theme release</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<h3>Showcase</h3>\n<p>Have you created nice website with this theme? Let us know!</p>\n<h3>Background color combinations included in the package:</h3>\n<p>White, grey, black, light blue, dark blue, light green, purple, gold and yellow. You can easily replace the background image in order to get other colors like red and violet as well.</p>\n<h3>Corporate Template can be used for any business:</h3>\n<p>Hotel &amp; hospitality, restaurant, real estate, marketing company, blog, cms, portfolio website, software &amp; computer sales, information technology, travel &amp; tourism, solicitors, car business, music industry, food &amp; drinks, human resources and personal relations organizations, school, university and college websites, science, magazine &amp; community websites, blog and many more.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:78:\"http://wordpressskins.org/1713/freestyle-responsive-wordpress-theme.html/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1:{s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1:\"0\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:8;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:63:\"\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n				\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n\n		\n		\n				\n			\n		\n		\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:5:{s:0:\"\";a:7:{s:5:\"title\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:38:\"Coreden – Responsive WordPress Theme\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:70:\"http://wordpressskins.org/1702/coreden-responsive-wordpress-theme.html\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:79:\"http://wordpressskins.org/1702/coreden-responsive-wordpress-theme.html#comments\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:7:\"pubDate\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:31:\"Wed, 20 Jun 2012 11:25:44 +0000\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_la