INSERT INTO `sat9Qy_posts` VALUES (4,1,'2013-03-18 05:56:11','2013-03-18 05:56:11','<a href=\"http://localhost/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2013/03/about-satluj1.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-274\" alt=\"about-satluj\" src=\"http://localhost/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2013/03/about-satluj1.jpg\" width=\"706\" height=\"173\" /></a>Satluj Public School is an independent, co-educational English medium institute of a rich reputation located within Panchkula, Haryana, which is adjacent to Chandigarh.\r\n\r\nThe school is run by “Satluj Educational Society”, which a registered entity, and which eminent personalities &amp; NRI’s on its governing body.\r\n\r\nThe founder and director is a visionary educationist, Shri. Pritam Singh Serai, who has taught in various schools and colleges in India, the United Kingdom (UK) and the United States of America (USA), and has an experience of over 60 years in education.\r\n\r\nThe present Principal, Shri. Krit Serai, is an eminent educationist with teaching experience of over 20 years in the UK, the USA and Indian education. He is a CBSE National Awardee, and one of the leaders at the forefront of the educational sector within the region.\r\n\r\nThe school was established on 12th January, 1976, and since then, has been imparting high-quality education to its students. With a rich tradition of nearly 40 years, Satluj has a strong alumni association, SESA, with members to the tune of over 10,000.\r\n\r\nThe school has a regular exchange program with educational institutions in the United Kingdom, and other countries.\r\n\r\nThe school is located in two purpose built campuses for Primary &amp; Senior Secondary classes in sectors 2 and 4, Panchkula, respectively, in an area of 12 acres.\r\n\r\nWith internationalism at its core, Satluj is ISO 9001:2008 Certified Institute, and strives to maintain that “Global Vision..is our Tradition”.','About Satluj','','publish','open','open','','about-satluj','','','2013-06-17 05:14:31','2013-06-17 04:14:31','',0,'http://localhost/wordpress/?page_id=4',0,'page','',0),(5,1,'2013-03-18 05:56:26','2013-03-18 05:56:26','At Satluj Public School, we are committed to offering the very best facilities and extend opportunities to students to grow in a competitive environment. With this view, Satluj Public School offers the following facilities.\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><span style=\"line-height: 14px;\">2 beautiful 12 acres campuses (separate for Junior and Senior Wing) with HUDA award winning gardens.</span></li>\r\n	<li>Three well equipped Science Laboratories with the latest uptodate apparatus.</li>\r\n	<li>Two new Computer Centers with Pentium Computers linked to a school wide network with visual display units and associated hardware, managed by professional company Microzone.</li>\r\n	<li>Art and Craft, Pottery area\' Drama studios including a poetry area.</li>\r\n	<li>Two large halls with excellent staging facilities and big open air stadia which can accommodate 2000 people.</li>\r\n	<li>Two well equipped libraries with the latest encyclopedia and publications and reference magazine sections.</li>\r\n	<li>One Home Science laboratory with the latest cooking appliances like microwave, gas cookers etc.</li>\r\n	<li>Audio-Visual equipment to teach pupils technically with the latest CD Rom/TV/Video/Video Drivers/Maps/3D Models/Projectors/Photocopiers etc. Purpose built LCD Multimedia Theatre.</li>\r\n	<li>Auditorium under construction</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>EXCELLENT SPORTING FACILITIES</strong></p>\r\nThe students have been actively participating in Sport events held in School and have also successfully represented our school at district, state and national levels. Satluj Public School has the best sporting facilities provided by a school in this region :-\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><span style=\"line-height: 14px;\">Snooker and Pool Club</span></li>\r\n	<li>Lawn Tennis Court</li>\r\n	<li>Basketball Stadium</li>\r\n	<li>All Weather Two Cricket Pitches</li>\r\n	<li>Three grounds for Soccer, Hockey, Handball, Volleyball</li>\r\n	<li>A 200 meters grass track</li>\r\n	<li>Swimming and Splash Pool</li>\r\n	<li>Horse Riding Club</li>\r\n	<li>Badminton Courts</li>\r\n	<li>Athletic Area</li>\r\n	<li>Fully equipped Gym and Fitness Centre.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<strong>FUTURE PLANS FOR FURTHER PROGRAMMES ARE ALREADY WELL ADVANCED AND WILL INCLUDE :-</strong>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><span style=\"line-height: 14px;\">Expansion of school with the state of the art furnishings and fittings.</span></li>\r\n	<li>80 additional class rooms to cater to the growing strength of the pupils. Target is 5000 pupils.</li>\r\n	<li>Additional Science laboratories, Home Science laboratory and Career and Counselling rooms.</li>\r\n	<li>Expansion of the day boarding programme.</li>\r\n	<li>Centrally fitted air conditioned and heated classrooms</li>\r\n	<li>Sports wings of Sports Authority of India.</li>\r\n	<li>Joining the NCC.</li>\r\n	<li>Latest collection of electronics toys and gazettes for the primary school children.</li>\r\n	<li>An international size auditorium</li>\r\n	<li>AC transport</li>\r\n	<li>Foreign and Indian University and College placements</li>\r\n	<li>Residential Hostel Plan</li>\r\n	<li>Regular foreign tours</li>\r\n</ul>','Facilities','','publish','open','open','','facilities','','','2013-06-17 06:33:33','2013-06-17 05:33:33','',0,'http://localhost/wordpress/?page_id=5',0,'page','',0),(6,1,'2013-03-18 05:56:35','2013-03-18 05:56:35','<h4>Vision:</h4>\r\nSatluj should be an ever-progressing premier educational institute in the context of times, imparting the highest quality of education to its students.\r\n<h4><strong>Mission:</strong></h4>\r\n<strong></strong> Satluj shall impart secular and ever-progressing to its students, and contribute to the upliftment of society at large.\r\n\r\n<img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-560\" alt=\"vision-mission\" src=\"http://localhost/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2013/03/vision-mission1.jpg\" width=\"638\" height=\"385\" />','Vision','','publish','open','open','','vision','','','2013-03-20 17:27:34','2013-03-20 15:27:34','',0,'http://localhost/wordpress/?page_id=6',0,'page','',0),(7,1,'2013-03-18 05:56:45','2013-03-18 05:56:45','<a href=\"http://localhost/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2013/03/DSC_3592.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-970\" alt=\"DSC_3592\" src=\"http://localhost/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2013/03/DSC_3592.jpg\" width=\"764\" height=\"509\" /></a>','Photo Gallery','','publish','open','open','','photo-gallery','','','2013-07-19 07:10:09','2013-07-19 06:10:09','',0,'http://localhost/wordpress/?page_id=7',0,'page','',0),(8,1,'2013-03-18 05:56:58','2013-03-18 05:56:58','[contact-form-7 id=\"564\" title=\"Contact form 1\"]','Online Registration 2013-14','','publish','open','open','','online-registration-2013-14','','','2013-03-25 12:39:38','2013-03-25 10:39:38','',0,'http://localhost/wordpress/?page_id=8',0,'page','',0),(9,1,'2013-03-18 05:57:11','2013-03-18 05:57:11','[table id=15 /]','Contact us','','publish','open','open','','contact-us','','','2013-03-19 17:21:38','2013-03-19 15:21:38','',0,'http://localhost/wordpress/?page_id=9',0,'page','',0),(10,1,'2013-03-18 05:57:09','2013-03-18 05:57:09','','Contact us','','inherit','open','open','','9-revision','','','2013-03-18 05:57:09','2013-03-18 05:57:09','',9,'http://localhost/wordpress/?p=10',0,'revision','',0),(11,1,'2013-03-18 05:57:25','2013-03-18 05:57:25','<h3>Mrs. J.K.Serai &amp; Mr. Pritam Singh Serai</h3>\r\nfounded the school in 1976. “Live with Effort”, is the motto of our school. We train our students to use ‘effort’ and ‘courage’ as tools to sharpen their personalities, mainly in four areas of human activity – intellectual, social-emotional, physical and moral. Our teachers make an all-out effort to develop our scholars to be physically strong, healthy, intellectually well above-average and morally reliable. Our goals of education are dynamic and infinite. We look towards our school as our focal point. Our opinion is that, one courageous, stable intelligent and reliable person is a “majority”.\r\n\r\n<img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-586\" alt=\"founders\" src=\"http://localhost/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2013/03/founders2.jpg\" width=\"600\" height=\"209\" />\r\n<h2><span style=\"font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.846153846;\">Director : Pritam Singh Serai</span></h2>\r\nM.A. History; B.Ed., M.A. Education (University of Lancaster, U.K.).\r\n\r\nPreviously, History Master at William Morris High School, London;\r\n\r\nProfessor of Education at Eastern Michigan University, USA; and\r\n\r\nLecturer in Education, Berkishire College of Education, Reading U.K.\r\n\r\nTara Chand SABOO Award 2009\r\nDEO/Governer Award','Founder','','publish','open','open','','founder','','','2013-06-17 06:04:18','2013-06-17 05:04:18','',0,'http://localhost/wordpress/?page_id=11',0,'page','',0),(12,1,'2013-03-18 05:57:34','2013-03-18 05:57:34','Satlujians are being shaped to become productive and proud citizens of our nation. They are taught to be morally sound, confident, up-to-date, technology sharp and scientifically advanced. Satlujians believe and achieve. The future belongs to such individuals. Satluj is a futuristic school.\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://localhost/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2013/03/sir.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-333\" alt=\"sir\" src=\"http://localhost/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2013/03/sir.jpg\" width=\"360\" height=\"498\" /></a>\r\n\r\nPrinicipal : Krit SeraiM.A. History, B.A. (Hons.) Geography, M.A. Education (University of London, U.K.).History &amp; Geography Courses from London School of Economics &amp; Cambridge University, U.K.;Educational Specialist Course, (Central Missouri State University, U.S.A.);Previously, Governor and Year Head at Stockwell Park School, London Borough of Lambeth, London;\r\n\r\nHead of Department, London Brough of Hounslow, London.\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://localhost/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2013/03/PRINCIPAL-AWARD-1.gif\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-334\" alt=\"PRINCIPAL-AWARD-1\" src=\"http://localhost/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2013/03/PRINCIPAL-AWARD-1.gif\" width=\"405\" height=\"218\" /></a>\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://localhost/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2013/03/Award-by-Sibble.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-335\" alt=\"Award by Sibble\" src=\"http://localhost/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2013/03/Award-by-Sibble.jpg\" width=\"405\" height=\"696\" /></a>\r\n\r\nCBSE National Award being received by Principal Krit Serai on 4th September 2011 by MHRD Mr. Kapil Sibal, MOS MHRD , Chairman CBSE at New Delhi.\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://localhost/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2013/03/DSC_0100-copy.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-907\" alt=\"DSC_0100 copy\" src=\"http://localhost/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2013/03/DSC_0100-copy.jpg\" width=\"420\" height=\"280\" /></a>\r\n<div id=\"wp_editbtns\" style=\"display: block; top: 888.367px; left: 283.5px;\">                    <strong> Principal Awarded by Governor on19th June,2013</strong></div>','Principal','','publish','open','open','','principal','','','2013-07-04 04:25:14','2013-07-04 03:25:14','',0,'http://localhost/wordpress/?page_id=12',0,'page','',0),(13,1,'2013-03-18 05:57:48','2013-03-18 05:57:48','Please do not edit.','Achievements','','publish','open','closed','','achievements','','','2013-07-01 07:14:19','2013-07-01 06:14:19','',0,'http://localhost/wordpress/?page_id=13',0,'page','',0),(14,1,'2013-03-18 05:57:57','2013-03-18 05:57:57','Satluj celebrated Annual Function “Satluj Pride 2011″ Chief Guest was Sh.Meher Mittal.\r\n\r\nThe school provides full opportunities to every child for his/her physical, mental &amp; moral development. The school offers a wide choice of co-curricular &amp; extra-curricular activities\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://localhost/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2013/03/Activities-1.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-313\" alt=\"Activities 1\" src=\"http://localhost/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2013/03/Activities-1.jpg\" width=\"420\" height=\"260\" /></a>S@tlujPubl!c\r\n[table id=7 /]\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://localhost/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2013/03/Activities-21.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-306\" alt=\"Activities 2\" src=\"http://localhost/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2013/03/Activities-21.jpg\" width=\"420\" height=\"260\" /></a>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n\r\n<strong>Co-Curricular Activities</strong>\r\n\r\nTo generate social interaction and develop creative skills, a student is expected to become a member of :-\r\n<a href=\"http://localhost/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2013/03/Activities-3.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-302\" alt=\"Activities 3\" src=\"http://localhost/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2013/03/Activities-3.jpg\" width=\"420\" height=\"260\" /></a>\r\n\r\n[table id=6 /]\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<strong>Committees</strong>\r\n\r\nThe management has appointed various committees to look after the affairs of the school which include :-\r\n\r\n[table id=5 /]','Activities','','publish','open','open','','activities','','','2013-07-08 11:13:05','2013-07-08 10:13:05','',0,'http://localhost/wordpress/?page_id=14',0,'page','',0),(15,1,'2013-03-18 05:58:30','2013-03-18 05:58:30','<strong>THE SCHOOL IS AN ISO 9001:2008 CERTIFIED INSTITUTE</strong>\r\n\r\n<strong>QUALITY POLICY</strong>\r\n\r\nTo continually upgrade system and processes of admission, teaching, learning, examination, evaluation, research and extension in order to become a globally recognised institute of academic excellence.\r\n\r\nOur aim is to enhance students satisfaction. We work on the motto “Live with Effort”\r\n\r\n<strong>Instruction :</strong>\r\n\r\nISO 9001:2008 Certificate is issued for maintaining international level quality system.\r\n\r\n<strong>SATLUJ IS ISO CERTIFIED</strong>\r\n\r\nBY MOODY UK an accredited certifying body.\r\n\r\nOur school is ISO 9001:2008 certified by ICL and we achieved this certificate for maintaining high quality management system and providing the best system to our students, with the aim to enhance students satisfaction.\r\n\r\n<strong>MANAGEMENT SYSTEM INCLUDES</strong>\r\n\r\n<strong>TO PROVIDE THE BEST:</strong>\r\n[table id=11 /]','ISO 9001:2008','','publish','open','open','','iso-90012008','','','2013-06-17 06:13:30','2013-06-17 05:13:30','',0,'http://localhost/wordpress/?page_id=15',0,'page','',0),(16,1,'2013-03-18 05:58:38','2013-03-18 05:58:38','<strong> School is a member of British Library</strong>\r\n<strong>British Library</strong>\r\nSCO 183-87, Sector 9-C,\r\nMadhya Marg, Chandigarh.\r\n<strong>Tel. Nos</strong>. 2745195/2745196\r\n<strong>Email</strong> : bl.chandigarh@in.britishcouncil.org\r\n<em><strong>www.britishcouncil.org.in</strong></em>\r\n\r\nSatluj Public School is an institutional member of British Library.\r\n\r\n1. <strong>What does it mean for Satlujians ?</strong>\r\n\r\n[table id=24 /]\r\n\r\n<img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-443\" alt=\"Cambridge 1\" src=\"http://localhost/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2013/03/Cambridge-1.jpg\" width=\"420\" height=\"260\" />\r\n\r\n<strong>School is a member of British Council</strong>\r\n\r\nBritish Council is the representative of UK in India and oversees all its institutions like Cambridge University Exams., Libraries/Seminars etc.\r\n\r\n2. <strong>What does it means for Satlujians ?</strong>\r\n\r\n[table id=25 /]\r\n\r\n<img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-447\" alt=\"Cambridge 2\" src=\"http://localhost/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2013/03/Cambridge-22.jpg\" width=\"420\" height=\"260\" />','Cambridge ESOL Exams','','publish','open','open','','cambridge-esol-exams','','','2013-06-17 05:35:47','2013-06-17 04:35:47','',0,'http://localhost/wordpress/?page_id=16',0,'page','',0),(17,1,'2013-03-18 05:58:49','2013-03-18 05:58:49','<img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-452\" alt=\"18\" src=\"http://localhost/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2013/03/18.jpg\" width=\"616\" height=\"397\" />\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img class=\"size-full wp-image-453 aligncenter\" alt=\"Smart Class Room\" src=\"http://localhost/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2013/03/Smart-Class-Room1.jpg\" width=\"510\" height=\"190\" /></p>','3D-Smart Class Room','','publish','open','open','','smart-class-room','','','2013-06-17 05:05:28','2013-06-17 04:05:28','',0,'http://localhost/wordpress/?page_id=17',0,'page','',0),(18,1,'2013-03-18 05:58:48','2013-03-18 05:58:48','','Smart Class Room','','inherit','open','open','','17-revision','','','2013-03-18 05:58:48','2013-03-18 05:58:48','',17,'http://localhost/wordpress/?p=18',0,'revision','',0),(19,1,'2013-03-18 05:59:01','2013-03-18 05:59:01','Satluj Public School Faculty use internationally proven techniques in educating our pupils. Here is a sample of some of the techniques used.\r\n\r\n[table id=18 /]\r\n\r\n<img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-460\" alt=\"Teaching Methodology 1\" src=\"http://localhost/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2013/03/Teaching-Methodology-11.jpg\" width=\"500\" height=\"372\" />\r\n\r\n<img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-461\" alt=\"Teaching Methodology 2\" src=\"http://localhost/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2013/03/Teaching-Methodology-2.jpg\" width=\"500\" height=\"372\" />\r\n\r\n&nbsp;','Teaching Methodology','','publish','open','open','','teaching-methodology','','','2013-03-20 07:33:24','2013-03-20 05:33:24','',0,'http://localhost/wordpress/?page_id=19',0,'page','',0),(20,1,'2013-03-18 05:59:09','2013-03-18 05:59:09','Satluj Public School has introduced this much needed facility. Parents have the option to opt either for inducting their wards as day-boarders or day-scholars. The facility will help working parents and pupils who want to fully participate in school activities. The following activities will be co-ordinated by the staff:-\r\n\r\n1. Solving of academic difficulties.\r\n\r\n2. Supervision of home work.\r\n\r\n3. Revision of class work.\r\n\r\n4. Special pre-unit test preparation facility.\r\n\r\n5. Additional Opportunities to undertake sport activities and hobbies.\r\n\r\n6. Nutritious and Healthy food and snacks\r\n\r\n<img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-465\" alt=\"Day-Boarding-Image\" src=\"http://localhost/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2013/03/Day-Boarding-Image1.jpg\" width=\"415\" height=\"285\" />\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n[table id=19 /]\r\n\r\n<img class=\"alignnone size-large wp-image-623\" alt=\"DOC3-page-0\" src=\"http://localhost/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2013/03/DOC3-page-0-706x997.jpg\" width=\"625\" height=\"882\" />','Day Boarding','','publish','open','open','','day-boarding','','','2013-06-17 05:59:06','2013-06-17 04:59:06','',0,'http://localhost/wordpress/?page_id=20',0,'page','',0),(21,1,'2013-03-18 05:59:18','2013-03-18 05:59:18','[table id=10 /]\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://localhost/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2013/03/Senior_Wing.jpg\"><img src=\"http://localhost/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2013/03/Senior_Wing.jpg\" alt=\"Senior_Wing\" width=\"465\" height=\"320\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-327\" /></a>\r\n\r\nOutdoor Facilities shady area, picnic areas, lush green parks, flowerbeds rose gardens etc.\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://localhost/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2013/03/SeniorWing51.jpg\"><img src=\"http://localhost/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2013/03/SeniorWing51.jpg\" alt=\"SeniorWing51\" width=\"465\" height=\"320\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-324\" /></a>\r\n\r\n[table id=9 /]\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://localhost/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2013/03/SeniorWing6.jpg\"><img src=\"http://localhost/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2013/03/SeniorWing6.jpg\" alt=\"SeniorWing6\" width=\"465\" height=\"320\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-319\" /></a>\r\n\r\n[table id=8 /]','Senior Wing','','publish','open','open','','senior-wing','','','2013-03-19 14:28:34','2013-03-19 1